dBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T08:36:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>3322 今年得2萬人 有1.5萬個學位<br />\n競爭少左 巴打加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d02d67b4f89a75895d0e098ca5efbea87f4a1aa3","tid":316511,"uid":46047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T08:39:41.000Z","msg":"聽日唔好就咁問有咩科岩讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁多科 點睇得哂<br />\n最好打自己分 + 自己Jupas排位<br />\n咁先有得比意見你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc66514ccf82a1f3bb1ac3e6db92985321096fe6","tid":316511,"uid":10140,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T08:41:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽日唔好就咁問有咩科岩讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁多科 點睇得哂<br />\n最好打自己分 + 自己Jupas排位<br />\n咁先有得比意見你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nOk 之前研究過幾個排法 今晚再研究下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cc87c13195623e7b4b3c505c557d49914716d29","tid":316511,"uid":42217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T08:45:26.000Z","msg":"JS1204 cityu cs 收全4 20分"},{"pid":"4b93ab8a6935de80e3b70872ea3d9b9d01341034","tid":316511,"uid":45055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T08:49:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>CU engine <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打係咪真？<br />\nd人話18 9分入到 但佢官網寫到勁高分 臨近放榜真係好緊張 已經分唔到邊啲人講真邊個講假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔好信 你唔好聽人講就排<br />\ncu engine 計weighting <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你呢個分9成入唔到<br />\n人地講完你都要自己去check下有冇weighting之類嫁嘛"},{"pid":"043cdc4a0a78ea24b408a11565d58fbf4ab212ae","tid":316511,"uid":46047,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T08:52:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>21分其實都有唔少選擇，poly都有啲科可以讀</blockquote><br />\n非3大sci/EDU/OU/asso同hd都有得諗<br />\n<br />\n樓主<br />\n任何5科最佳成績\t21<br />\n中英加最佳3科\t20<br />\n4個必修+1個最佳選修科\t20<br />\n4個必修+2個最佳選修科\t24<br />\n<br />\n而上年polyu best 5收大約21分既科有:<br />\nJS3002\t應用科學\t\t\t\t<br />\nJS3351\t運輸系統工程學\t\t\t<br />\nJS3363\t投資科學\t\t\t<br />\nJS3375\t環境工程與可持續發展學\t\t\t\t<br />\nJS3442\t物業管理學\t\t\t<br />\nJS3519\t互聯網及多媒體科技\t\t\t\t<br />\nJS3868\t電子計算\t\t\t\t<br />\nJS3703\t電子及資訊工程學\t\t<br />\nJS3557\t產品及工業工程\t\t\t\t<br />\nJS3985\t工程物理學\t\t\t\t<br />\nJS3492\t服裝及紡織\t\t\t\t<br />\n<br />\n但除左 服裝及紡織,電子計算 同產品及工業工程 多位D之外,其他都係得1X-2X個位<br />\n而且要食正weighting就只有 工程物理學 係穩,服裝及紡織 同電子計算 可以博<br />\n其他科就真係要睇下樓主升唔升到分先可以考慮<br />\n祝樓主聽日升到分,入到想入既科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dbcc4cc88cbd39924e5c909160df767aca49bd6","tid":316511,"uid":106489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T10:10:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>21分其實都有唔少選擇，poly都有啲科可以讀</blockquote><br />\n巴打有冇咩科建議 真係想萬無一失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打你想讀咩科先？ 文？ 理？商？ 定係為學校名氣或者前途？<br />\n<br />\n英文3我覺得唔搏cu engine好啲， 搏下poly或者city engine會大機會啲。<br />\n同埋上面巴打講嘅poly 嘅科都可以考慮，因為今年考生少左，所以機會再大啲。<br />\n為錢途嘅話就可以考慮下ou sssdp nursing之類，不過睇下你願唔願意入非八大嘅學校，始終呢啲學校嘅名都唔好得去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n（上年為錢途入左ou，同親戚食飯都儘量唔講學校嘅話題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）"},{"pid":"8abeb4bea2b92e5b4338a1e570b552b19b53f087","tid":316511,"uid":28515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T10:13:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>21分其實都有唔少選擇，poly都有啲科可以讀</blockquote><br />\n非3大sci/EDU/OU/asso同hd都有得諗<br />\n<br />\n樓主<br />\n任何5科最佳成績\t21<br />\n中英加最佳3科\t20<br />\n4個必修+1個最佳選修科\t20<br />\n4個必修+2個最佳選修科\t24<br />\n<br />\n而上年polyu best 5收大約21分既科有:<br />\nJS3002\t應用科學\t\t\t\t<br />\nJS3351\t運輸系統工程學\t\t\t<br />\nJS3363\t投資科學\t\t\t<br />\nJS3375\t環境工程與可持續發展學\t\t\t\t<br />\nJS3442\t物業管理學\t\t\t<br />\nJS3519\t互聯網及多媒體科技\t\t\t\t<br />\nJS3868\t電子計算\t\t\t\t<br />\nJS3703\t電子及資訊工程學\t\t<br />\nJS3557\t產品及工業工程\t\t\t\t<br />\nJS3985\t工程物理學\t\t\t\t<br />\nJS3492\t服裝及紡織\t\t\t\t<br />\n<br />\n但除左 服裝及紡織,電子計算 同產品及工業工程 多位D之外,其他都係得1X-2X個位<br />\n而且要食正weighting就只有 工程物理學 係穩,服裝及紡織 同電子計算 可以博<br />\n其他科就真係要睇下樓主升唔升到分先可以考慮<br />\n祝樓主聽日升到分,入到想入既科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n噤錯負皮sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}